title: Higher Expectations?
description:
Pablo Torre and Domonique Foxworth debate which team has higher expectations: The Rams or the Bills, how LeBron, AD, & Russ feel about Pat Bev’s comments yesterday and what the chances are that people in Baton Rouge are already sick of Brian Kelly.
